es-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb9%2F2c%2Fd1f60df34808b5dac6d2736c8625%2Fpp-tr-ales-and-trails-prime-desert-woodland-preserve-60.jpg 1200w"  sizes="85vw"    width="1200"   height="800"  src="https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/830fdf2/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/1200x800!/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb9%2F2c%2Fd1f60df34808b5dac6d2736c8625%2Fpp-tr-ales-and-trails-prime-desert-woodland-preserve-60.jpg" decoding="async"  loading="lazy"  >  </picture>   <div class="figure-content"> <div class="figure-credit">(Matt Pawlik)</div> </div>  </figure> </div>   </div>  </div><div class="poi-module-flex container-content"><div class="poi-module-flex container-content-block">  <h2 class="title poi-module-title"> Prime Desert Woodland Preserve </h2>  <div class="poi-module-categories"><span class="poi-module-categories-icon"><span class="icon category parks-trails-icon-fff"></span> </span><span class="neighborhood poi-module-categories-neighborhood"> Lancaster </span>  <span class="poi-module-categories-hike-type"> Desert Trail </span>   </div>  <div class="poi-module-hike poi-module-social">  <div class="poi-module-hike-distance"><span class="icon poi-module-hike-icon-ruler-000" aria-label="distance"></span> <span>3.0-mile loop</span></div>   <div class="poi-module-hike-difficulty"><span class="icon poi-module-hike-icon-gauge-000" aria-label="difficulty"></span> <span>Easy</span></div>   <div class="poi-module-hike-elevation"><span class="icon poi-module-hike-icon-mountain-000" aria-label="elevation"></span> <span>25 feet</span></div>  </div>     <div data-element="description" class="ct-body-1 ct-rich-text-children font-service font-light text-base mt-3">Start at the Elyze Clifford Interpretive Center at the preserve. Free parking. Dog-friendly.<br><br><b>Distance from brewery:</b> 3.3 miles and <b>distance from</b> <b>winery:</b> 4.2 miles</div>    <div class="postal-address"><svg class="icon postal-address-icon map-marker"><use xlink:href="#icon-map-marker"></use></svg><div><a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=34.653329%2C-118.192013" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="street postal-address-street"> 43201 35th St. W, </span><span class="city postal-address-city"> Lancaster, </span><span class="state postal-address-state"> California </span><span class="zipcode postal-address-zipcode"> 93536 </span></a></div></div> <div class="poi-module-more-info"> More Info </div></div></div></div> </div>   <div class="column-container-column three-column-container-column" data-click="3col2"> <div class="module poi-module" data-click="poi"  data-map-marker-id="0000017d-1603-dd2a-a1ff-5ebf456c0000"   data-map-marker-longitude="-118.14568"   data-map-marker-latitude="34.65903"   data-map-marker-title="Brävery Brewing"   data-module-neighborhood="Lancaster"      data-module-cuisines="Brewery"    data-module-category="restaurants" data-module-id="0000017d-2b4b-d6d5-ad7f-efdba3a50000"><div class="poi-module-flex container-media">  <div class="media poi-module-media">   <div class="image poi-module-image"> <figure class="figure"> <picture >    <source  type="image/webp"  srcset="https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/53129d8/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/320x213!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F2d%2F53%2Fd342e693408b929ca6a11e619dfe%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-bravery-brewing.JPG 320w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/3bd6fb7/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/568x379!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F2d%2F53%2Fd342e693408b929ca6a11e619dfe%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-bravery-brewing.JPG 568w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/3030bf1/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/768x512!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-bright