="city postal-address-city"> Los Angeles, </span><span class="state postal-address-state"> California </span><span class="zipcode postal-address-zipcode"> 90012 </span></a></div></div> <div class="poi-module-more-info"> More Info </div></div></div></div> </div>   <div class="column-container-column two-column-container-5050-column" data-click="5050col2"> <div class="module poi-module" data-click="poi"  data-map-marker-id="0000017c-f1d1-d757-affd-f3dbba820001"   data-map-marker-longitude="-118.227653"   data-map-marker-latitude="34.069181"   data-map-marker-title="Angeleno Wine Co."   data-module-neighborhood="Chinatown"      data-module-cuisines="Brewery"    data-module-category="restaurants" data-module-id="0000017c-f1d1-dc45-a57c-f5f3a56a0000"><div class="poi-module-flex container-media">  <div class="media poi-module-media">   <div class="image poi-module-image"> <figure class="figure"> <picture >    <source  type="image/webp"  srcset="https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/a2ce6d8/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/320x213!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff3%2Fcf%2Ff826fb034e7d85d4f61e573b4e6d%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-angeleno-wine.jpg 320w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/f4a8764/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/568x379!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff3%2Fcf%2Ff826fb034e7d85d4f61e573b4e6d%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-angeleno-wine.jpg 568w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/1d4b3f6/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/768x512!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff3%2Fcf%2Ff826fb034e7d85d4f61e573b4e6d%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-angeleno-wine.jpg 768w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/87354b2/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/1024x683!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff3%2Fcf%2Ff826fb034e7d85d4f61e573b4e6d%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-angeleno-wine.jpg 1024w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/bc558d0/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/1200x800!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff3%2Fcf%2Ff826fb034e7d85d4f61e573b4e6d%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-angeleno-wine.jpg 1200w"  sizes="85vw"  >     <img class="image" alt="Bottles of wine on a barrel"  srcset="https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/0cb0393/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/320x213!/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff3%2Fcf%2Ff826fb034e7d85d4f61e573b4e6d%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-angeleno-wine.jpg 320w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/b0ac53c/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/568x379!/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff3%2Fcf%2Ff826fb034e7d85d4f61e573b4e6d%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-angeleno-wine.jpg 568w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/a46bd96/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/768x512!/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff3%2Fcf%2Ff826fb034e7d85d4f61e573b4e6d%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-angeleno-wine.jpg 768w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/bc3a0de/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/1024x683!/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff3%2Fcf%2Ff826fb034e7d85d4f61e573b4e6d%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-angeleno-wine.jpg 1024w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/ee57716/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/1200x800!/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff3%2Fcf%2Ff826fb034e7d85d4f61e573b4e6d%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-angeleno-wine.jpg 1200w"  sizes="85vw"    width="1200"   height="800"  src="https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/ee57716/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/1200x800!/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ff3%2Fcf%2Ff826fb034e7d85d4f61e573b4e6d%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-angeleno-wine.jpg" decoding="async"  loading="lazy"  >  </picture>   <div class="figure-content"> <div class="figure-credit">(Matt Pawlik)</div> </div>  </figure> </div>   </div>  </div><div class="poi-module-flex container-content"><div class="poi-module-flex container-content-block">  <h2 class="title poi-module-title"> Angeleno Wine Co. </h2>  <div class="poi-module-categories"><span class="poi-module-categories-icon"><span class="icon category restaurants-icon-fff"></span> </span><span class="neighborhood poi-module-categories-neighborhood"> Chinatown </span>   <span class="cuisine poi-module-categories-cuisine"> Brewery </span>    </div>        <div data-element="description" class="ct-body-1 ct-rich-text-children font-service font-light text-base mt-3"><b>Our favorite 🍷: </b>Superbloom (white), Swayze Vineyard Alicante Bouschet, The Meadow Rosé<br><br><b>Hours:</b> noon to 8 p.m. Saturdays; noon to 6 p.m. Sundays</div>    <div class="social poi-module-social">   <div class="website poi-module-website"><span class="icon globe-icon-087da1"></span> <a class="link" href="https://www.angelenowine.com/" target="_blank" >website</a> </div>   <div class="instagram poi-module-instagram"><span class="icon instagram-icon-087da1"></span> <a class="link" href="https://instagram.com/angelenowine" target="_blank" >instagram</a> </div>  </div>  <div class="postal-address"><svg class="icon postal-address-icon map-marker"><use xlink:href="#icon-map-marker"></use></svg><div><a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=34.069181%2C-118.227653" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="street postal-address-street"> 1646 N. Spring St., </span><span class="city postal-address-city"> Los Angeles, </span><span class="state postal-address-state"> California </span><span class="zipcode postal-address-zipcode"> 90012 </span></a></div></div> <div class="poi-module-more-info"> More Info </div></div></div></div> </div>  </div></div>   </div><p> </p><p>Big views, beautiful trees, city history? How about city views, big trees and beautiful history? No matter which way you say it, Elysian Park, L.A.’s oldest green space, has it all. </p> <p>Explore the city’s third-largest park along the West Loop (with options to extend). Find the trailhead on a large, palm-dotted lawn at the northwest corner of Elysian Park Drive and Stadium Way. It begins in a dense eucalyptus grove. In fact, most of the park’s original 150,000 trees planted in 1886 are trees native to Australia. The trail soon leaves the forest and meanders along the canyon wall, providing panoramic city views over the L.A. River, the 5 Freeway and beyond. As the trail makes a U-turn, you ascend nearly 200 feet, providing a great mid-hike workout and a secret reward: the Marion Harlow Memorial Grove. Continue southwest before making a hairpin turn and connecting with the Chavez Ravine Arboretum grounds. The area still contains some labeled specimens (like the pink coral tree) to enjoy before you head back to the trailhead. To double your distance, cross Stadium Way to find the 2.8-mile Portola Loop, which features more downtown vistas, especially at Angels Point, which overlooks Dodger Stadium. </p> <p>For a glass (or two) of wine afterward, go to <a class="link" href="https://www.angelenowine.com/" target="_blank" >Angeleno Wine Co.</a> at the southeast corner of the park and enjoy offerings with a focus on Spanish varietals.</p> </div>   </div>  </div><div class="story-stack-item" id="6" data-target ><div class="story-stack-item-number"  data-hide-number ><span>6</span></div>  <div  class="story-stack-story">  <h3 class="story-stack-story-title">Griffith Park and Paperback Brewing Co.</h3>     <div data-element="story-stack-story-body" class="ct-rich-text-children font-body font-normal text-lg leading-7.75 text-primary-text-color clearfix"> <div class="enhancement" data-click="enhancement"
    
        data-align-center
    
>   <div class="column-container two-column-container-5050" >  <div class="column-container-row two-column-container-5050-row">  <div class="column-container-column two-column-container-5050-column" data-click="5050col1"> <div class="module poi-module" data-click="poi"  data-map-marker-id="0000017d-0c06-d6ef-a9fd-cd6f9ef40000"   data-map-marker-longitude="-118.30786"   data-map-marker-latitude="34.1125"   data-map-marker-title="Griffith Park"   data-module-neighborhood="Griffith Park"     data-module-hike-difficulty="Moderate"     data-module-hike-length="5.25"   data-module-category="parks-trails" data-module-subcategory="Urban Trail" data-module-subcategory-filter-id="parks-trails_00000178-1e5a-dff5-abff-de5a13ce0000" data-module-id="0000017d-0c06-dd2a-a1ff-4cbe6a340000"><div class="poi-module-flex container-media">  <div class="media poi-module-media">   <div class="image poi-module-image"> <figure class="figure"> <picture >    <source  type="image/webp"  srcset="https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/a697a27/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4000x2667+0+1667/resize/320x213!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F26%2F00%2F68a365ec4ff6ad7cfa7175e2bd9e%2F870221-la-tr-ales-and-trails-griffith-park-4-als.JPG 320w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/3874055/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4000x2667+0+1667/resize/568x379!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F26%2F00%2F68a365ec4ff6ad7cfa7175e2bd9e%2F870221-la-tr-ales-and-trails-griffith-park-4-als.JPG 568w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/26d0bd3/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4000x2667+0+1667/resize/768x512!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F26%2F00%2F68a365ec4ff6ad7cfa7175e2bd9e%2F870221-la-tr-ales-and-trails-griffith-park-4-als.JPG 768w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/c6d0ff3/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4000x2667+0+1667/res