0786" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="street postal-address-street"> 5375 Red Oak Drive, </span><span class="city postal-address-city"> Los Angeles, </span><span class="state postal-address-state"> California </span><span class="zipcode postal-address-zipcode"> 90068 </span></a></div></div> <div class="poi-module-more-info"> More Info </div></div></div></div> </div>   <div class="column-container-column two-column-container-5050-column" data-click="5050col2"> <div class="module poi-module" data-click="poi"  data-map-marker-id="0000017d-0c0b-dd2a-a1ff-4cbf8b080000"   data-map-marker-longitude="-118.261888"   data-map-marker-latitude="34.130089"   data-map-marker-title="Paperback Brewing Co."   data-module-neighborhood="Glendale"      data-module-cuisines="Brewery"    data-module-category="restaurants" data-module-id="0000017d-0c0b-d502-a1ff-ad4f7c260000"><div class="poi-module-flex container-media">  <div class="media poi-module-media">   <div class="image poi-module-image"> <figure class="figure"> <picture >    <source  type="image/webp"  srcset="https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/148d5f5/2147483647/strip/true/crop/3024x2016+0+1008/resize/320x213!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F08%2Ff7%2F6f429bbd49dd85a2c28a5061048f%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-paperback.jpg 320w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/bd1ac12/2147483647/strip/true/crop/3024x2016+0+1008/resize/568x379!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F08%2Ff7%2F6f429bbd49dd85a2c28a5061048f%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-paperback.jpg 568w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/84ff6d1/2147483647/strip/true/crop/3024x2016+0+1008/resize/768x512!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F08%2Ff7%2F6f429bbd49dd85a2c28a5061048f%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-paperback.jpg 768w,http