os-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-eagle-rock-brewery.jpg 1024w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/f73454c/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/1200x800!/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F88%2F37%2F1b6c283d4ec1b078420e81ea83fc%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-eagle-rock-brewery.jpg 1200w"  sizes="85vw"    width="1200"   height="800"  src="https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/f73454c/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/1200x800!/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F88%2F37%2F1b6c283d4ec1b078420e81ea83fc%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-eagle-rock-brewery.jpg" decoding="async"  loading="lazy"  >  </picture>   <div class="figure-content"> <div class="figure-credit">(Matt Pawlik)</div> </div>  </figure> </div>   </div>  </div><div class="poi-module-flex container-content"><div class="poi-module-flex container-content-block">  <h2 class="title poi-module-title"> Eagle Rock Brewery </h2>  <div class="poi-module-categories"><span class="poi-module-categories-icon"><span class="icon category restaurants-icon-fff"></span> </span><span class="neighborhood poi-module-categories-neighborhood"> Glassell Park </span>   <span class="cuisine poi-module-categories-cuisine"> Brewery </span>    </div>        <div data-element="description" class="ct-body-1 ct-rich-text-children font-service font-light text-base mt-3"><b>Our favorite 🍺:</b> Manifesto (Witbier), Populist (IPA), Amwolf (German Pilsner)<br><br><b>Hours:</b> 3 to 9 p.m. Wednesdays to Fridays; noon to 9 p.m. Saturdays; noon to 7 p.m. Sundays</div>    <div class="social poi-module-social">  <div class="phone poi-module-phone"><span class="icon phone-icon-087da1" aria-label="phone"></span> <a class="link phone" href="tel:3232577866" data-social-service="phone" >(323) 257-7866 </a> </div>   <div class="website poi-module-website"><span class="icon globe-icon-087da1"></span> <a class="link" href="http://www.eaglerockbrewery.com/" target="_blank" >website</a> </div>   <div class="instagram poi-module-instagram"><span class="icon instagram-icon-087da1"></span> <a class="link" href="https://instagram.com/eaglerockbrew" target="_blank" >instagram</a> </div>  </div>  <div class="postal-address"><svg class="icon postal-address-icon map-marker"><use xlink:href="#icon-map-marker"></use></svg><div><a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=34.11505%2C-118.24352" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="street postal-address-street"> 3056 Roswell St., </span><span class="city postal-address-city"> Los Angeles, </span><span class="state postal-address-state"> California </span><span class="zipcode postal-address-zipcode"> 90065 </span></a></div></div> <div class="poi-module-more-info"> More Info </div></div></div></div> </div>  </div></div>   </div><p> </p><p>Looking for a quick post-work, pre-drinks workout? Head to Eagle Rock Canyon for a 1-mile loop that visits the neighborhood’s dome-shaped landmark named for the ridge that resembles the winged predator. </p> <p>The perch near the top offers soaring views of the downtown L.A. skyline, the rolling hills of Hollywood and Metropolitan Water District open space below. The path is narrow and climbs quickly through chaparral staples, such as sugarbush, scrub oak, sage and the taco-shaped leaves of laurel sumac. Being this close to the Eagle Rock itself is cool, but it’s a tough angle to catch when the shadow makes the eagle indent appear to be in flight. </p> <p>After descending, head to the namesake brewery of the hipster haven — <a class="link" href="http://www.eaglerockbrewery.com/" target="_blank" >Eagle Rock Brewery</a> — which opened in 2009. Try its classics or rotating offerings, grab some grub from a visiting food truck and enjoy the good vibes. Other nearby options: Relentless Brewing &amp; Spirits, an Eagle Rock transplant from Temecula that specializes in tangy sours. Rock on!</p> </div>   </div>  </div><div class="story-stack-item" id="9" data-target ><div class="story-stack-item-number"  data-hide-number ><span>9</span></div>  <div  class="story-stack-story">  <h3 class="story-stack-story-title">Los Angeles River Walk and Frogtown Brewery</h3>     <div data-element="story-stack-story-body" class="ct-rich-text-children font-body font-normal text-lg leading-7.75 text-primary-text-color clearfix"> <div class="enhancement" data-click="enhancement"
    
