-marker"><use xlink:href="#icon-map-marker"></use></svg><div><a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=34.123219%2C-118.166237" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="street postal-address-street"> 221 San Pascual Ave., </span><span class="city postal-address-city"> South Pasadena, </span><span class="state postal-address-state"> California </span><span class="zipcode postal-address-zipcode"> 91030 </span></a></div></div> <div class="poi-module-more-info"> More Info </div></div></div></div> </div>   <div class="column-container-column two-column-container-5050-column" data-click="5050col2"> <div class="module poi-module" data-click="poi"  data-map-marker-id="0000017c-f136-df3c-a3ff-f1b7c8310000"   data-map-marker-longitude="-118.15329"   data-map-marker-latitude="34.13841"   data-map-marker-title="Cervecería del Pueblo"   data-module-neighborhood="Pasadena"      data-module-cuisines="Brewery"    data-module-category="restaurants" data-module-id="0000017c-f136-dc45-a57c-f536b5240000"><div class="poi-module-flex container-media">  <div class="media poi-module-media">   <div class="image poi-module-image"> <figure class="figure"> <picture >    <source  type="image/webp"  srcset="https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/8cfdecb/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/320x213!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5e%2F01%2Fd905cdc645b4949183ddd014e809%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-cerveceria-del-pueblo.jpg 320w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/e6c918a/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/568x379!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5e%2F01%2Fd905cdc645b4949183ddd014e809%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-cerveceria-del-pueblo.jpg 568w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/f6763a9/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/768x512!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-ti