ead. $10 admission with parking. Dogs aren’t allowed.<br><br><b>Distance from brewery:</b> 1.2 miles</div>    <div class="postal-address"><svg class="icon postal-address-icon map-marker"><use xlink:href="#icon-map-marker"></use></svg><div><a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=34.11602%2C-117.719074" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="street postal-address-street"> 1500 N. College Ave., </span><span class="city postal-address-city"> Claremont, </span><span class="state postal-address-state"> California </span><span class="zipcode postal-address-zipcode"> 91711 </span></a></div></div> <div class="poi-module-more-info"> More Info </div></div></div></div> </div>   <div class="column-container-column two-column-container-5050-column" data-click="5050col2"> <div class="module poi-module" data-click="poi"  data-map-marker-id="0000017d-14d3-d502-a1ff-bdd7d53a0000"   data-map-marker-longitude="-117.701847"   data-map-marker-latitude="34.108969"   data-map-marker-title="Claremont Craft Ales"   data-module-neighborhood="Claremont"      data-module-cuisines="Brewery"    data-module-category="restaurants" data-module-id="0000017d-14d3-d3be-a57d-3ef3c6e10000"><div class="poi-module-flex container-media">  <div class="media poi-module-media">   <div class="image poi-module-image"> <figure class="figure"> <picture >    <source  type="image/webp"  srcset="https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/8edcf3f/2147483647/strip/true/crop/3024x2016+0+477/resize/320x213!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F8d%2F54%2F531aac1c41199ca55c3b30f8106e%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-claremont-breweries-63.JPG 320w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/0686bc5/2147483647/strip/true/crop/3024x2016+0+477/resize/568x379!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F8d%2F54%2F531aac1c41199ca55c3b30f8106e%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-claremont-breweries-63.JPG 