ita Canyon Road, </span><span class="city postal-address-city"> Newhall, </span><span class="state postal-address-state"> California </span><span class="zipcode postal-address-zipcode"> 91321 </span></a></div></div> <div class="poi-module-more-info"> More Info </div></div></div></div> </div>   <div class="column-container-column two-column-container-5050-column" data-click="5050col2"> <div class="module poi-module" data-click="poi"  data-map-marker-id="0000017d-14c9-dd2a-a1ff-5cff26e10000"   data-map-marker-longitude="-118.52969"   data-map-marker-latitude="34.38093"   data-map-marker-title="Brewery Draconum"   data-module-neighborhood="Santa Clarita"      data-module-cuisines="Brewery"    data-module-category="restaurants" data-module-id="0000017d-14c8-d3be-a57d-3ee9b2480000"><div class="poi-module-flex container-media">  <div class="media poi-module-media">   <div class="image poi-module-image"> <figure class="figure"> <picture >    <source  type="image/webp"  srcset="https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/487493b/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/320x213!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F08%2F6e%2F0a0e47074cc5842f56955d7fba6f%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-draconum.jpg 320w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/9062646/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/568x379!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F08%2F6e%2F0a0e47074cc5842f56955d7fba6f%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-draconum.jpg 568w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/55d1858/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/resize/768x512!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F08%2F6e%2F0a0e47074cc5842f56955d7fba6f%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-draconum.jpg 768w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/c8f2753/2147483647/strip/true/crop/4032x2688+0+168/