 day). Dogs are not allowed on trails.<br><br><b>Distance from winery:</b> 5.8 miles</div>    <div class="postal-address"><svg class="icon postal-address-icon map-marker"><use xlink:href="#icon-map-marker"></use></svg><div><a href="https://maps.apple.com/?q=34.10468%2C-118.7118" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="street postal-address-street"> 1925 Las Virgenes Road, </span><span class="city postal-address-city"> Calabasas, </span><span class="state postal-address-state"> California </span><span class="zipcode postal-address-zipcode"> 91302 </span></a></div></div> <div class="poi-module-more-info"> More Info </div></div></div></div> </div>   <div class="column-container-column two-column-container-5050-column" data-click="5050col2"> <div class="module poi-module" data-click="poi"  data-map-marker-id="0000017d-1150-d502-a1ff-bd5795520000"   data-map-marker-longitude="-118.777936"   data-map-marker-latitude="34.114466"   data-map-marker-title="Cornell Winery &amp; Tasting Room"   data-module-neighborhood="Unincorporated Santa Monica Mountains"      data-module-cuisines="Winery"    data-module-category="restaurants" data-module-id="0000017d-1150-d6ef-a9fd-d97f27450000"><div class="poi-module-flex container-media">  <div class="media poi-module-media">   <div class="image poi-module-image"> <figure class="figure"> <picture >    <source  type="image/webp"  srcset="https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/7b9708b/2147483647/strip/true/crop/3534x2356+0+1600/resize/320x213!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F92%2Fc6%2F22d565484d4fb16883715c6c2cf5%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-cornell-winery-66.JPG 320w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/2304727/2147483647/strip/true/crop/3534x2356+0+1600/resize/568x379!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F92%2Fc6%2F22d565484d4fb16883715c6c2cf5%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-cornel