el Mar, </span><span class="city postal-address-city"> San Pedro, </span><span class="state postal-address-state"> California </span><span class="zipcode postal-address-zipcode"> 90731 </span></a></div></div> <div class="poi-module-more-info"> More Info </div></div></div></div> </div>   <div class="column-container-column two-column-container-5050-column" data-click="5050col2"> <div class="module poi-module" data-click="poi"  data-map-marker-id="0000017d-115a-dd2a-a1ff-59fe9bbe0001"   data-map-marker-longitude="-118.280513"   data-map-marker-latitude="33.72689"   data-map-marker-title="Brouwerij West"   data-module-neighborhood="San Pedro"      data-module-cuisines="Brewery"    data-module-category="restaurants" data-module-id="0000017d-115a-d502-a1ff-bd5f75b70000"><div class="poi-module-flex container-media">  <div class="media poi-module-media">   <div class="image poi-module-image"> <figure class="figure"> <picture >    <source  type="image/webp"  srcset="https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/9d20f1f/2147483647/strip/true/crop/3264x2176+0+136/resize/320x213!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F3c%2F52%2F71a8fe76437bb0f1bf7426a5ccdf%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-san-pedro-breweries.jpg 320w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/3c7795b/2147483647/strip/true/crop/3264x2176+0+136/resize/568x379!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F3c%2F52%2F71a8fe76437bb0f1bf7426a5ccdf%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-san-pedro-breweries.jpg 568w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/2629156/2147483647/strip/true/crop/3264x2176+0+136/resize/768x512!/format/webp/quality/80/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F3c%2F52%2F71a8fe76437bb0f1bf7426a5ccdf%2Fla-photos-handouts-la-tr-ales-and-trails-san-pedro-breweries.jpg 768w,https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/0e705ce/2147483647/strip/true/